<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=devise-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>tomokura</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="header">
      <div class="title_img">
        <%= link_to root_path, class:"title_imag" do %>
          <%= image_tag 'TOMOKURA.png', class:'title' %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <ul class="header_sign_up">
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <li><%= link_to '太郎さん', root_path, class: "user_nickname" %>
          <li><%= link_to 'ログアウト', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "logout" %></li>
        <% else %>
          <li><%= link_to '新規登録', new_user_registration_path, class:"sign_up" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to 'ログイン', new_user_session_path, class:"log_in" %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="main">
      <ul class="back_img">
        <li><%= image_tag 'dish.jpg', class:'dish' %></li>
        <li><%= image_tag 'flowers.jpg', class:'flowers' %></li>
        <li><%= image_tag 'sentakumono.jpg', class:'sentakumono' %></li>
        <li><%= image_tag 'recipi.jpg', class:'recipi' %></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="title_section">
        <section>
          <p>大切な人と、お金の管理で揉めないように、
          <br>最初に決めよう。暮らしの決まりごと。</p>
          <div>
            <ul class="sign_up">
              <li><%= link_to '新規登録', new_user_registration_path, class: "sign-up" %></li>
              <li><%= link_to 'ログイン', new_user_session_path, class: "login" %></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>